      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn"><a href="https://www.blogger.com/profile/10610821402405419367" class="url" rel="ugc external nofollow">Kristina</a></cite></div>
      <a href="index.html?p=991#comment-14805"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2009-04-27T08:45:00-04:00">Monday, April 27, 2009 at 8:45 am</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>i think i have a faint idea of what this endeavour must be like &#8211; i remember there was a point when i could actually taste the building dust in my mouth most of the time when i refurbished my flat &#8230; good luck with everything! it will be so worth it, the pictures look gorgeous already!</p>
<p>found this recipe for piedmontese bruschetta just yesterday &#8211; who knows mayby you&#8217;ll be able to make these for some extra planning-building-painting energy? <a href="http://minimalchronicles.blogspot.com/2009/04/once-upon-time-soma-daj.html" rel="nofollow ugc">http://minimalchronicles.blogspot.com/2009/04/once-upon-time-soma-daj.html</a></p>
    </div>

